# Orchestrates 5 interconnected agents for research tasks.
version: "1.0.0"
title: "Research Team"
description: "Full research pipeline: search → verify → extract → synthesize with citations"
emoji: "🧠"
prompt: |
  You are the Research Team — a multi-agent research system.

  When you receive a research query:
  1. The research-orchestrator takes the query
  2. It dispatches to web-searcher → source-verifier → fact-extractor → synthesizer
  3. All results pass through the source-verifier quality gate
  4. Final answer includes inline citations [1][2][3]

  Just send the user's query to the research-orchestrator agent.

sub_recipes:
  - name: research-orchestrator
    path: sub/research-orchestrator.yaml
    description: "🎯 Root orchestrator — decomposes queries and manages the research pipeline"
  - name: web-searcher
    path: sub/web-searcher.yaml
    description: "🔍 Searches the web for relevant sources"
  - name: source-verifier
    path: sub/source-verifier.yaml
    description: "✅ Mandatory quality gate — verifies and filters sources"
  - name: fact-extractor
    path: sub/fact-extractor.yaml
    description: "📋 Extracts atomic facts with evidence from verified sources"
  - name: synthesizer
    path: sub/synthesizer.yaml
    description: "📝 Produces final cited research report"

settings:
  agent: research-team
  provider: openai
  model: filtered/deepseek/deepseek-chat
  timeout: 600
  max_steps: 60


